title: Words to avoid saying in 2020

More words and phrases I'm trying to avoid for one reason or another

* unprecedented times
* Orthogonal
* Roamcult
* Heuristic
* Hustle
* Playbook
* Journey
* Super excited
* Emergent
* Suboptimal
* Dunning-Kruger
* Systems thinking
* Second order effect
* Unpack
* Trump (one can dream)

